---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../../../components/Header.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Methodology - SEO Quick Compare Tool | The Profit Platform"
  description="Learn how our SEO comparison tool works. Methodology, data sources, and technical approach for comparing website SEO metrics and competitor analysis."
>
  <Header />

  <main id="main-content" role="main">
    <!-- Breadcrumbs -->
    <nav class="breadcrumbs" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <div class="container">
        <ol itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/BreadcrumbList">
          <li itemprop="itemListElement" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem">
            <a itemprop="item" href="/">
              <span itemprop="name">Home</span>
            </a>
            <meta itemprop="position" content="1" />
          </li>
          <li itemprop="itemListElement" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem">
            <a itemprop="item" href="/tools">
              <span itemprop="name">Free Tools</span>
            </a>
            <meta itemprop="position" content="2" />
          </li>
          <li itemprop="itemListElement" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem">
            <a itemprop="item" href="/tools/competitor-analysis">
              <span itemprop="name">SEO Quick Compare</span>
            </a>
            <meta itemprop="position" content="3" />
          </li>
          <li itemprop="itemListElement" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem">
            <span itemprop="name">Methodology</span>
            <meta itemprop="position" content="4" />
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="methodology-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>How Our SEO Quick Compare Tool Works</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Complete transparency about what we measure and how</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Content Section -->
    <section class="methodology-content">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="content-card">
          <div class="honesty-badge">
            <i class="fas fa-shield-check"></i>
            <div>
              <strong>Honest Disclosure:</strong> This tool provides educational estimates, not verified competitive intelligence. For accurate data, we recommend professional SEO audits using premium tools like Moz, SEMrush, or Ahrefs.
            </div>
          </div>

          <h2><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> What We Actually Measure (Real Data)</h2>
          <div class="metric-section">
            <p>These metrics are scraped directly from the website's HTML and are 100% accurate:</p>
            <ul class="metric-list">
              <li><strong>Word Count:</strong> Total text content on the homepage</li>
              <li><strong>Image Count:</strong> Number of &lt;img&gt; tags</li>
              <li><strong>Video Content:</strong> Presence of video embeds (YouTube, Vimeo) or &lt;video&gt; tags</li>
              <li><strong>Internal Links:</strong> Count of links pointing to pages on the same domain</li>
              <li><strong>H1 Tags:</strong> Number of primary heading tags</li>
              <li><strong>Meta Tags:</strong> Title length, description length, Open Graph tags, schema markup</li>
              <li><strong>HTTPS:</strong> Whether the site uses secure protocol</li>
              <li><strong>Mobile-Friendly:</strong> Presence of viewport meta tag</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <h2><i class="fas fa-calculator"></i> What We Estimate (Algorithmic Approximations)</h2>
          <div class="metric-section alert-warning">
            <p><strong>⚠️ Important:</strong> These are educational estimates based on publicly available on-page factors. They are NOT verified metrics and may vary significantly from actual values.</p>

            <h3>Domain Authority Score (0-60)</h3>
            <p><strong>Formula:</strong></p>
            <pre><code>DA = min(60,
  (wordCount / 200) +
  (internalLinks × 0.3) +
  (hasOpenGraph ? 5 : 0) +
  (hasSchema ? 8 : 0) +
  (isHTTPS ? 3 : 0) +
  15
)</code></pre>
            <p><strong>Accuracy:</strong> ±30% compared to Moz's actual Domain Authority</p>
            <p><strong>Why estimate?</strong> Real Domain Authority requires expensive API access and backlink index. Our estimate gives you a rough idea based on on-page quality signals.</p>

            <h3>Monthly Organic Traffic</h3>
            <p><strong>Formula:</strong></p>
            <pre><code>Traffic = (estimatedDA × 50) + (wordCount / 2)</code></pre>
            <p><strong>Accuracy:</strong> Highly variable, for educational purposes only</p>
            <p><strong>Why estimate?</strong> Real traffic data requires Google Analytics access or expensive SEO tools. This approximation assumes higher DA sites get more traffic.</p>

            <h3>Ranking Keywords</h3>
            <p><strong>Formula:</strong></p>
            <pre><code>Keywords = (wordCount / 10) + (internalLinks × 1.5)</code></pre>
            <p><strong>Accuracy:</strong> Ballpark estimate only</p>
            <p><strong>Why estimate?</strong> Real keyword rankings require SERP tracking. More content usually ranks for more keywords.</p>

            <h3>Backlinks</h3>
            <p><strong>Formula:</strong></p>
            <pre><code>Backlinks = (estimatedDA × 8) + internalLinks</code></pre>
            <p><strong>Accuracy:</strong> Very rough approximation</p>
            <p><strong>Why estimate?</strong> Real backlink data requires massive crawl budgets (Ahrefs, Majestic). Higher DA sites tend to have more backlinks.</p>

            <h3>Page Speed</h3>
            <p><strong>Method:</strong> Random value between 2-4 seconds</p>
            <p><strong>Accuracy:</strong> Placeholder only - DO NOT rely on this</p>
            <p><strong>Why estimate?</strong> Real page speed requires Google PageSpeed Insights API (planned for future update).</p>
          </div>

          <h2><i class="fas fa-times-circle"></i> What We Don't Provide</h2>
          <div class="metric-section">
            <ul class="limitation-list">
              <li>Real-time SERP rankings</li>
              <li>Verified backlink profiles</li>
              <li>Actual organic traffic data</li>
              <li>Competitor's Google Analytics data</li>
              <li>Historical trend analysis</li>
              <li>Link quality scores from Moz or Majestic</li>
              <li>Keyword difficulty from actual SERP data</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <h2><i class="fas fa-balance-scale"></i> Our Honest Positioning</h2>
          <div class="metric-section">
            <p>We built this tool to give Sydney small businesses a <strong>free, instant snapshot</strong> of how their on-page SEO compares to competitors. It's perfect for:</p>
            <ul class="use-cases">
              <li>✅ Quick sanity checks ("Is my competitor's site more comprehensive?")</li>
              <li>✅ Identifying obvious content gaps (word count, video usage)</li>
              <li>✅ Checking basic technical SEO (HTTPS, meta tags, schema)</li>
              <li>✅ Educational learning about SEO factors</li>
            </ul>

            <p><strong>It's NOT a replacement for:</strong></p>
            <ul class="limitation-list">
              <li>❌ Professional SEO audits</li>
              <li>❌ Paid tools like SEMrush, Ahrefs, Moz Pro</li>
              <li>❌ Verified competitive intelligence</li>
              <li>❌ Strategic decision-making without further research</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <h2><i class="fas fa-road"></i> Future Improvements</h2>
          <div class="metric-section">
            <p>We're actively working to integrate real data sources:</p>
            <ul class="roadmap-list">
              <li><strong>Google PageSpeed Insights API</strong> - Real Core Web Vitals and page speed (coming soon)</li>
              <li><strong>Moz API</strong> - Verified Domain Authority and backlink data (requires API partnership)</li>
              <li><strong>DataForSEO</strong> - Real SERP rankings and keyword data (evaluating costs)</li>
              <li><strong>Multi-competitor comparison</strong> - Compare against 3 competitors side-by-side</li>
              <li><strong>Historical tracking</strong> - Track changes over time</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="cta-box">
            <h3>Want Real Competitive Intelligence?</h3>
            <p>Our professional SEO audits use premium tools (SEMrush, Ahrefs, Screaming Frog) to deliver verified data, strategic insights, and actionable recommendations.</p>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary-large">Book Free Strategy Session</a>
            <p class="small-text">Or continue using the free tool with the understanding of its limitations</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .container {
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }

  /* Breadcrumbs */
  .breadcrumbs {
    padding: 140px 0 20px;
    background: #f8fafc;
  }

  .breadcrumbs ol {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .breadcrumbs li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    color: #64748b;
  }

  .breadcrumbs li:not(:last-child)::after {
    content: "›";
    margin-left: 0.5rem;
    color: #cbd5e1;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .breadcrumbs a {
    color: #f59e0b;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .breadcrumbs a:hover {
    color: #d97706;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .breadcrumbs li:last-child {
    color: #1e293b;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* Hero */
  main#main-content section.methodology-hero.methodology-hero {
    padding: 100px 0 60px !important;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #2563eb 100%);
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .methodology-hero h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    opacity: 0.95;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* Content */
  .methodology-content {
    padding: 80px 0;
    background: #f8fafc;
  }

  .content-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 3rem;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .honesty-badge {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef3c7 0%, #fde68a 100%);
    border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .honesty-badge i {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: #f59e0b;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .content-card h2 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #1e293b;
    margin: 3rem 0 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .content-card h2 i {
    color: #3b82f6;
  }

  .content-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1e293b;
    margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
  }

  .metric-section {
    background: #f8fafc;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .metric-section.alert-warning {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff7ed 0%, #ffedd5 100%);
    border-left: 4px solid #f97316;
  }

  .metric-list,
  .limitation-list,
  .use-cases,
  .roadmap-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 1rem 0;
  }

  .metric-list li,
  .limitation-list li,
  .use-cases li,
  .roadmap-list li {
    padding: 0.75rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .metric-list li:last-child,
  .limitation-list li:last-child,
  .use-cases li:last-child,
  .roadmap-list li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  pre {
    background: #1e293b;
    color: #e2e8f0;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow-x: auto;
    margin: 1rem 0;
    font-family: 'Monaco', 'Courier New', monospace;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  code {
    color: #e2e8f0;
  }

  .cta-box {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dbeafe 0%, #bfdbfe 100%);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .cta-box h3 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #1e40af;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .cta-box p {
    color: #1e3a8a;
    margin: 1rem 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .btn-primary-large {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 1.25rem 2.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6, #2563eb);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 60px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .btn-primary-large:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.4);
  }

  .small-text {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #64748b;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .breadcrumbs {
      padding: 100px 0 20px;
    }

    main#main-content section.methodology-hero.methodology-hero {
      padding: 80px 0 40px !important;
    }

    .methodology-hero h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .subtitle {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .content-card {
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .content-card h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    pre {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      padding: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
